data.description: Custom built ranch home on a full unfinished basement sits on over 7 acres. Beautiful hardwood and tile floors. Granite and marble thru-out. Oversized bedrooms. Self cleaning, jetted garden tub and separate shower in master. Hugh laundry room. Custom kitchen with built in wall ovens and smooth cooktop, breakfast nook and separate dining room. Office/flex space. Full unfinished daylight basement stubbed for bathroom. Additional 2 car garage/workshop. Beautiful home surrounded by old growth trees. Great investment opportunity with possible assemblage for 15-17 acres.
